episodes.synopsis: Nation-less, strapped for resources and fueled only by determination, Che and other rebels engages in swift, bloody battle to free the Cuban people from the corrupt dictatorship of Fulgencio Batista.
episodes.title: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Following his successes in Cuba, Che travels to Bolivia and recruits another band of guerilla fighters in the harsh jungles. They embark upon a mission to spark revolution throughout Latin America.
episodes.title: Part 2

video.title: Che
video.synopsis: Benicio Del Toro stars as Ernesto "Che" Guevara, an Argentine doctor who became one of Latin America's most iconic revolutionary leaders in the 1950s.
